Anthony Y. DELISLE, Sr., Appellant, v. Roberta MYERS; Myers Properties, Appellees. No. 04-1740. United States Court of Appeals, Eighth Circuit. Submitted July 19, 2004. Decided July 28, 2004. Anthony V. DeLisle, Sr., Des Moines, IA, pro se.

Before MELLOY, LAY, and COLLOTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Anthony DeLisle appeals the district court’s1 dismissal for lack of subject matter jurisdiction of his civil claim against his landlord. Upon de novo review, we affirm for the reasons stated by the district court. See 8th Cir. R. 47B.

. The Honorable Ronald E. Longstaff, Chief Judge, United States District Court for the Southern District of Iowa.
